  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've got a part-time job looking after pets while the owner is away.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4464630/extras/080369b06632f0e4f37f7083ab08cdd0.avif?t=1773738556\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4464630/extras_big/080369b06632f0e4f37f7083ab08cdd0.webp?t=1773738556 width=1560 height=878 /></span>\"FEED\" is a bite-sized retro point-and-click puzzle game. It features multiple puzzles and a touch of cult horror.<br><br>Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay & Controls: A retro point-and-click puzzle game that's easy to pick up.<br>Puzzle Design: Semi-open puzzles to solve within a house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backstory: A cult story with horror elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Length: Takes about 30 minutes to complete without a guide.</p>",
