      "review_text": "I really didn't expect too much when I started playing this game. But it actually caught me by surprise and turned out to be a solid puzzle game. The atmosphere and setting are cool and really hook you in. Puzzles are also well done. However, the game is very short lasting only about 45 minutes. I would love to see this project fully developed into an actual full length game. I would purchase it for sure. This developer has some talent.",
